1
00:01:21,320 --> 00:01:23,560
Let's begin, Dr. G.

2
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:29,720
You shouldn't

3
00:01:29,760 --> 00:01:31,840
ask a friend for therapy.

4
00:01:32,680 --> 00:01:34,200
Only people who've been through pain

5
00:01:34,200 --> 00:01:36,130
can relate to other people's pain.

6
00:01:36,840 --> 00:01:37,720
No one

7
00:01:38,120 --> 00:01:39,440
can heal me except you.

8
00:01:39,720 --> 00:01:40,880
You're strong.

9
00:01:40,880 --> 00:01:42,340
Do you really need my help?

10
00:01:42,800 --> 00:01:44,640
Even the strongest ones have weaknesses,

11
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:46,039
and only you

12
00:01:47,160 --> 00:01:48,039
know mine.

13
00:01:50,759 --> 00:01:51,560
Fine.

14
00:01:52,440 --> 00:01:53,400
Close your eyes.

15
00:01:58,800 --> 00:02:01,320
Have you been eating raw meat lately?

16
00:02:02,960 --> 00:02:03,560
Yes.

17
00:02:03,920 --> 00:02:04,880
When?

18
00:02:06,160 --> 00:02:06,960
This morning.

19
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:15,440
Did that

20
00:02:15,920 --> 00:02:17,400
make you feel any better?

21
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:31,160
No.

22
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:38,200
Relax.

23
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:40,120
Relax.

24
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:43,000
Take a deep breath.

25
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:46,880
Imagine

26
00:02:47,200 --> 00:02:49,440
you're in a dark tunnel.

27
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,460
There's a warm white light

28
00:02:51,640 --> 00:02:53,200
at the end of the tunnel.

29
00:02:54,200 --> 00:02:58,000
You slowly walk towards the light,

30
00:02:59,160 --> 00:03:00,240
and in the light,

31
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:03,260
you'll see the answer deep in your heart.

32
00:03:08,760 --> 00:03:09,560
What's wrong?

33
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:11,080
What did you see?

34
00:03:28,640 --> 00:03:31,700
Are the nightmares of the Lu family
still haunting you?

35
00:03:32,200 --> 00:03:32,930
Not anymore.

36
00:03:35,079 --> 00:03:35,840
Really?

37
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:39,400
You know,

38
00:03:40,040 --> 00:03:41,320
the cemetery is just their leverage.

39
00:03:41,320 --> 00:03:43,180
He won't touch it unless he has to.

40
00:03:43,520 --> 00:03:45,520
Why are you still doing what he says?

41
00:03:47,120 --> 00:03:49,250
Is it because you still care about him?

42
00:03:51,440 --> 00:03:52,200
No.

43
00:03:57,760 --> 00:03:58,440
Su Xia,

44
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:00,560
look at me.

45
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:04,520
Su Xia, where are you?

46
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:07,360
Get here in 10 minutes.

47
00:04:08,160 --> 00:04:10,480
Y-You answered the call.

48
00:04:11,640 --> 00:04:12,570
My hand slipped.

49
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:16,040
You just got me into big trouble.

50
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:18,839
Su Xia.

51
00:04:22,079 --> 00:04:24,360
You came back for your dad, right?

52
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:26,800
Of course.

53
00:04:26,960 --> 00:04:27,760
Okay.

54
00:04:28,320 --> 00:04:29,800
I'll let you handle this

55
00:04:29,800 --> 00:04:30,960
your way.

56
00:04:31,280 --> 00:04:33,080
But if you stray from the path,

57
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:35,960
I'll get you straight myself.

58
00:04:42,760 --> 00:04:43,690
I'll see you off.

59
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:02,560
Su Xia,

60
00:05:03,640 --> 00:05:05,240
remember what I said.

61
00:05:12,600 --> 00:05:13,320
Su Xia,

62
00:05:13,880 --> 00:05:14,680
come home.

63
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:21,920
Lu Fan.

64
00:05:23,840 --> 00:05:24,960
You're so pathetic

65
00:05:24,960 --> 00:05:26,240
right now.

66
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:27,600
Is using violence

67
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:28,840
the only way you can keep her

68
00:05:28,840 --> 00:05:30,080
by your side?

69
00:05:31,640 --> 00:05:33,170
I'll say this one last time.

70
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:34,280
Come home.

71
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:31,760
Lu Fan, be a man

72
00:06:31,760 --> 00:06:32,360
and come at me.

73
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:33,920
Don't let them hurt Xiao Qi!

74
00:06:33,960 --> 00:06:35,800
Mr. Lu, Han Qi is here.

75
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:37,460
He's waiting in the study.

76
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:45,280
Get out.

77
00:06:45,320 --> 00:06:46,120
Mr. Lu.

78
00:06:47,080 --> 00:06:49,120
The cemetery project starts now.

79
00:06:50,760 --> 00:06:51,620
Thanks, Mr. Lu.

80
00:06:58,600 --> 00:06:59,159
Fine.

81
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:00,280
Dig it up.

82
00:07:04,400 --> 00:07:05,200
Today,

83
00:07:06,680 --> 00:07:08,840
I'll dig up your father's grave.

84
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:15,290
What will you do?

85
00:07:15,880 --> 00:07:17,200
What can you do?

86
00:07:17,440 --> 00:07:18,240
You're right.

87
00:07:18,720 --> 00:07:19,760
What can I do?

88
00:07:20,840 --> 00:07:23,400
Today, you're going to
dig up my family's grave.

89
00:07:23,400 --> 00:07:24,760
So, who's next?

90
00:07:25,400 --> 00:07:28,080
Shouldn't your family's grave
be cleaned up too?

91
00:07:28,080 --> 00:07:29,120
I'm curious.

92
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:32,040
Was your father just as confident

93
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:33,280
as you are now?

94
00:07:35,840 --> 00:07:37,170
Are you threatening me?

95
00:07:38,880 --> 00:07:39,800
With my family

96
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:41,400
and my father?

97
00:07:44,640 --> 00:07:45,480
No.

98
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:49,720
It was just a friendly reminder.

99
00:07:50,200 --> 00:07:51,000
Lu Fan,

100
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:53,040
sometimes, anger

101
00:07:53,440 --> 00:07:54,960
makes people stupid

102
00:07:56,480 --> 00:07:58,800
and pathetic.

103
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:03,280
Now,

104
00:08:03,680 --> 00:08:05,340
listen to your own heartbeat.

105
00:08:05,880 --> 00:08:08,240
It's pounding so hard
like it's about to explode.

106
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:09,560
My father's grave

107
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:11,560
isn't the problem.

108
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:14,120
You should worry about

109
00:08:14,400 --> 00:08:16,730
when you will dig up
the grave in your heart

110
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:18,440
with your own stupidity.

111
00:08:30,320 --> 00:08:31,380
Trying to set me up?

112
00:08:35,640 --> 00:08:36,970
Who do you think you are?

113
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:41,120
You're nothing

114
00:08:42,799 --> 00:08:44,039
but a plaything to me.

115
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:47,320
Your life

116
00:08:47,320 --> 00:08:49,000
is in my hands now!

117
00:08:52,720 --> 00:08:53,520
A plaything?

118
00:08:54,680 --> 00:08:55,480
That's right.

119
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:57,420
Then why are you so scared?

120
00:08:57,560 --> 00:08:59,820
Are you afraid that you can't control me,

121
00:09:00,400 --> 00:09:02,400
or that you can't control yourself?

122
00:09:05,400 --> 00:09:06,120
Brother,

123
00:09:07,280 --> 00:09:08,160
do you think

124
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:11,040
your father was as obsessed

125
00:09:11,680 --> 00:09:13,920
with my sister back then

126
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:15,440
as you are with me now?

127
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:24,160
Shut up,

128
00:09:24,800 --> 00:09:26,080
you vixen.

129
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:30,160
Xiao Qi was right.

130
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:32,680
Stop chasing the same

131
00:09:32,680 --> 00:09:34,560
disgusting fantasy your father had.

132
00:09:34,560 --> 00:09:36,000
Go ahead and dig it!

133
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:37,480
Let's wait and see

134
00:09:37,640 --> 00:09:39,370
who's actually buried inside.

135
00:09:41,440 --> 00:09:42,280
Interesting.

136
00:09:44,240 --> 00:09:46,280
Su Xia, this is who you really are.

137
00:09:47,760 --> 00:09:49,880
How could someone
who brought down the Lu family

138
00:09:49,880 --> 00:09:51,480
be a meek little lamb?

139
00:09:58,960 --> 00:10:01,120
Now this is getting interesting.

140
00:10:02,560 --> 00:10:03,280
Isn't it,

141
00:10:04,400 --> 00:10:05,360
dear sister?

142
00:10:41,560 --> 00:10:42,360
Ms. Su.

143
00:10:44,040 --> 00:10:45,500
It's good to see you again.

144
00:10:47,520 --> 00:10:49,850
Mr. Han, shouldn't you be at the cemetery?

145
00:10:50,120 --> 00:10:51,780
It's just the project launch.

146
00:10:51,840 --> 00:10:53,300
I can handle it with a call.

147
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:55,040
No need to go there in person.

148
00:10:55,720 --> 00:10:56,520
Ms. Su,

149
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:59,240
my family has prepared

150
00:10:59,640 --> 00:11:01,720
for this project for three years.

151
00:11:02,880 --> 00:11:04,520
Now, our words finally

152
00:11:05,560 --> 00:11:07,480
mean something to Mr. Lu.

153
00:11:13,240 --> 00:11:14,000
Ms. Su,

154
00:11:14,440 --> 00:11:16,560
you didn't deny it,

155
00:11:17,160 --> 00:11:18,280
but deep down,

156
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:20,290
you don't agree, do you?

157
00:11:29,480 --> 00:11:30,960
Did Lu Fan send you here?

158
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:32,520
No, no, no.

159
00:11:33,760 --> 00:11:37,720
I really want to help you
get through this.

160
00:11:40,560 --> 00:11:44,200
Mr. Han, how are you going to help me?

161
00:11:46,040 --> 00:11:47,000
Ouch, ouch!

162
00:11:47,480 --> 00:11:49,240
You never learn, do you?

163
00:11:52,880 --> 00:11:54,740
Clear your head and think it over!

164
00:11:56,160 --> 00:11:57,320
I can't swim!

165
00:12:01,440 --> 00:12:02,040
Mr. Lu.

166
00:12:07,920 --> 00:12:09,080
Mr. Lu, I'm sorry!

167
00:12:10,880 --> 00:12:11,840
Mr. Lu, I'm so sorry!

168
00:12:11,840 --> 00:12:13,100
I'll never do it again!

169
00:12:13,640 --> 00:12:14,320
What did you do wrong?

170
00:12:14,320 --> 00:12:17,280
I-I shouldn't have touched her!

171
00:12:17,680 --> 00:12:18,360
Mr. Lu.

172
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:21,000
I-I shouldn't have seen her as a plaything

173
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:22,480
and taken advantage of her!

174
00:12:22,480 --> 00:12:23,200
Mr. Lu, I'm sorry!

175
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:24,040
I'll never do it again!

176
00:12:24,040 --> 00:12:25,520
Mr. Lu, please have mercy!

177
00:12:25,520 --> 00:12:26,160
Mr. Lu...

178
00:12:29,440 --> 00:12:30,080
Mr. Lu...

179
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:34,640
If I remember correctly,

180
00:12:36,400 --> 00:12:38,800
you touched her with this hand.

181
00:12:39,840 --> 00:12:41,000
This hand...

182
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:45,120
I don't remember, Mr. Lu!

183
00:12:57,400 --> 00:12:59,330
But you were right about one thing.

184
00:13:00,080 --> 00:13:01,280
She's a plaything,

185
00:13:02,320 --> 00:13:04,160
but she's mine.

186
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:17,640
Spread the word.

187
00:13:18,840 --> 00:13:20,570
Whoever dares to treat his hand

188
00:13:21,360 --> 00:13:22,600
is my enemy.
